node.text: “We don’t see enough stories told by Black folks about Black people”- @aspire4gr8ness , #QueenCollective director shares her thoughts on the importance of widening our view at #Tribeca2021. Don’t miss you chance to watch all four Queen Collective documentaries @BET. For full details, visit the link in our bio. #WidentheScreen
